<br>
Questions: <br>
<br>
1. Has it been verified that the MS-III pet can cast the same DS as the Epic Pet?<br>
<br>
2. Does anyone know what % of the MS-III pets get such a DS?<br>
<br>
3. How long in time must I wait for a MS-III pet that has the EPIC pet DS to cast such? (...10 sec....30 sec.....3 days?)<br>
<br>
